{meta: title I Don't Mind Saying}
{meta: artist Charlie Walker}
{meta: composer Raymond Page}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]I don't mind [F]saying I've been lonesome 
For those [C]kisses that I've known
Don't mind [G7]saying I've been crying 
Just because I'm all [C]alone
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
I'd be [F]lying if I told you 
I don't [C]miss you anymore
Don't mind [G7]saying I'd be glad to see you 
Walking through that [C]door
{end_of_verse}

